 ays\; for you live and reign with the Father and the Holy Spirit\, one God\
 , now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  The virgin will be wi
 th child and will give birth to a son\, and they will call him Immanuel.  A
 lleluia.  (Matthew 1:23)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        23      O Come\, O 
 Come\, Emmanuel\n\nColor:  Blue or Purple\n\n
