 diation of your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you
  and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nA
 lleluia.  Now faith is being sure of what we hope for and certain of what w
 e do not see.  Alleluia.  (Hebrews 11:1)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        352
      Lord\, Enthroned in Heavenly Splendor\n\nColor:  Green
