 luia.  The Spirit of the Lord is on me\; he has anointed me to preach good 
 news.  Alleluia.  (Luke 4:18)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n395Seek Where You May to
  Find a Way or\n556Rise\, Shine\, You People\n\nColor:  Green\n\n
