 t\, your Son\, our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit
 \, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nAlleluia.  Jesus said\,
  “I am the light of the world.  Whoever follows me will never walk in darkn
 ess\, but will have the light of life.”  Alleluia.  (John 8:12)\n\nHymn of 
 the Day:\n93Hail to the Lord’s Anointed \n\nColor:  Green\n\n
