 r of the Day:\nAlmighty God\, we confess that we deserve to be punished for
  our evil deeds.  But we ask you graciously to cleanse us from all sin and 
 to comfort us with your salvation\; through your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lor
 d\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and f
 orever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nFor God so loved the world that he gave his o
 ne and only Son\, that whoever believes in him shall not perish but have et
 ernal life.  (John 3:16)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n391God Loved the World So tha
 t He Gave\n\nColor:  Purple\n\n
