DESCRIPTION:The Nativity of Our Lord—Christmas Eve \n\nLessons and Psalm:\n
       Isaiah 9:2-7\n      Titus 2:11-14\n      Luke 2:1-20\n      Psalm 96 
 \n\nPrayer of the Day: \n\nAlmighty God\, you made this holy night shine wi
 th the brightness of the true light.  Grant that as we have known on earth 
 the wonder of that light\, we may also behold him in all glory in the life 
 to come\; through your only Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and rei
 gns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of t
 he Day: \n\nAlleluia.  Today in the town of David a Savior has been born to
  you\; he is Christ the Lord.  Alleluia.  (Luke 2:11) \n\nHymn of the Day:\
 n      38        From Heaven Above to Earth I Come or\n      37        Once
  Again My Heart Rejoices \n\nColor:  White \n\n
