 ugh Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spir
 it\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n\nAlleluia.  We saw 
 his star in the east and have come to worship him.  Alleluia.  (Matthew 2:2
 b) \n\nHymn of the Day:\n        79              How Lovely Shines the Morn
 ing Star \n\nColor:  White \n\n
