 m in his path\, so may we always hail him as our King and follow him with p
 erfect confidence\; who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one
  God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n\nThe hour has come for the 
 Son of Man to be glorified.  (John 12:23) \n\nHymn of the Day:\n        132
 \, 133        Ride On\, Ride On in Majesty \n\nColor:  Purple \n\n
