 al Lectionary:\n\n      1 Kings 18:16-45\n\n\nPrayer of the Day: \n\nO God\
 , you form the minds of your faithful people in to a single will.  Make us 
 love what you command and desire what you promise\, that among the many cha
 nges of this world\, our hearts may ever yearn for the lasting joys of heav
 en\; through your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with y
 ou and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n
 \nAlleluia.  Alleluia.  Christ is risen!  He is risen indeed!  Alleluia.  I
  am the way\, the truth\, and the life\, says the Lord.  Alleluia.  (John 1
 4:6)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n      141               At the Lamb’s High Feast 
 We Sing \n\nColor:  White \n\n
