 icken by God\, smitten by him\, and afflicted.  (Isaiah 53:4)\n\nHymn of th
 e Day:\n      100     A Lamb Goes Uncomplaining Forth or\n      140       G
 od Was There on Calvary \n\nColor:  Black \n\n
