 illing obedience\; through your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord.\n\nVerse of th
 e Day: \n\nAlleluia.  Give thanks to the Lord\, for he is good.  His love e
 ndures forever.  Alleluia.  (Psalm 136:1) \n\nColor:  White \n
