 ng and reigning\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  Holy\
 , holy\, holy is the Lord Almighty\; the whole earth is full of his glory. 
  Alleluia.  (Isaiah 6:3b)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        177\,178 Come\, Ho
 ly Ghost\, Creator Blest\n\nColor:  White\n\n
