 ans 10:13-17\n\nPrayer of the Day\n\n     Almighty God\, you sent your one 
 and only Son as the Word of life for our eyes to see and our ears to hear. 
 Help us to believe what the Scriptures proclaim about him and do the things
  that are pleasing in your sight\; through Jesus Christ\, your Son\, our Lo
 rd\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and 
 forever.\n\nVerse of the Day\n\n     Alleluia. Jesus said\, “I am the light
  of the world. Whoever follows me will never walk in darkness\, but will ha
 ve the light of life.” Alleluia. (John 8:12 cf. NIV)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\
 n     93 Hail to the Lord’s Anointed\n\nColor: Green
