 od\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  We saw his star in
  the east and have come to worship him.  Alleluia.  (Matthew 2:2b)\n\nHymn 
 of the Day:\n\n        79      How Lovely Shines the Morning Star\n\nColor:
