 n\n        2 Corinthians 5:20b-6:2\n\n        Luke 18:9-14\n\n        Psalm
  51a\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        2 Samuel 24:10-25\n\n        Re
 velation 3:14-22\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty and merciful God\, you n
 ever despise what you have made and always forgive those who turn to you.  
 Create in us such new and contrite hearts that we may truly repent of our s
 ins and obtain your full and gracious pardon\; through your Son\, Jesus Chr
 ist our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\
 , now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nReturn to the Lord\, your God\, 
 for he is gracious and merciful\, slow to anger\, and abounding in steadfas
 t love.  (Joel 2:13)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        396     In Adam We Have
  All Been One\n\nColor:  Black or Purple\n\n
