 \n\n        Psalm 67\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        2 Thessalonians
  2:13-17\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty God\, you gave your one and only
  Son to be the light of the world.  Grant that your people\, illumined by y
