 y:\n\n        2 Corinthians 3:12-4:2\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nLord God\, be
 fore the suffering and death of your one and only Son\, you revealed his gl
 ory on the holy mountain.  Grant that we who bear his cross on earth may be
 hold by faith the light of his heavenly glory and so be changed into his li
 keness\; through Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and 
