 ia.  A voice came from the cloud: “This is my Son\, whom I love.  Listen to
  him!”   Alleluia.  (Mark 9:7b)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        97      Down
  from the Mount of Glory\n\nColor:  White\n\n
