 ah 9:9\,10\nPhilippians 2:5-11\nMark 11:1-10\nPsalm 24\n\nSupplemental Lect
 ionary:\n\nPrayer of the Day:\nWe praise you\, O God\, for the great acts o
 f love by which you redeemed us through your Son\, Jesus Christ.  As he was
  acclaimed by those who scattered their garments and branches of palm in hi
 s path\, so may we always hail him as our King and follow him with perfect 
