 now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nThe hour has come for the Son of Man
  to be glorified.  (John 12:23)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n132\, 133Ride On\, Rid
 e On in Majesty\n\nColor:  Purple\n\n
