 \n        Exodus 15:1-11\n\n        1 Corinthians 15:1-11\n\n        Luke 2
 4:1-12\n\n        Psalm 118\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty God\, by the 
 glorious resurrection of your Son Jesus Christ you conquered death and open
 ed the gate to eternal life.  Grant that we\, who have been raised with him
  through baptism\, may walk in the newness of life and ever rejoice in the 
 hope of sharing his glory\; through Jesus Christ our Lord\, to whom\, with 
 you and the Holy Spirit be dominion and praise now and forever.\n\nVerse of
  the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  Alleluia.  Christ is risen!  He is risen indeed!  A
 lleluia.  This is the day the Lord has made\; let us rejoice and be glad in
  it.  Alleluia.  (Psalm 118:24)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        156     Awak
 e\, My Heart\, with Gladness or\n\n        161     Christ Jesus Lay in Deat
 h’s Strong Bands\n\nColor:  White or Gold
