  forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nAlleluia.  Lord\, to whom shall we go?  You
  have the words of eternal life.  Alleluia.  (John 6:68)\n\nHymn of the Day
 :\n410Our Father\, Who from Heaven Above\n\nColor:  Green\n
