 gns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of t
 he Day: \n\nAlleluia.  Today in the town of David a Savior has been born to
  you\; he is Christ the Lord.  Alleluia.  (Luke 2:11) \n\nHymn of the Day:\
 n      38        From Heaven Above to Earth I Come or\n      37        Once
  Again My Heart Rejoices \n\nColor:  White
