 n\n        2 Corinthians 5:20b-6:2\n\n        Luke 18:9-14\n\n        Psalm
  51a\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        2 Samuel 12:1-13\n\n        Act
 s 5:1-11\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty and merciful God\, you never des
 pise what you have made and always forgive those who turn to you.  Create i
 n us such new and contrite hearts that we may truly repent of our sins and 
 obtain your full and gracious pardon\; through your Son\, Jesus Christ our 
 Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now an
 d forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nReturn to the Lord\, your God\, for he i
 s gracious and merciful\, slow to anger\, and abounding in steadfast love. 
  (Joel 2:13)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        396     In Adam We Have All Bee
 n One\n\nColor:  Black or Purple\n\n
