  reign with the Father and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\n
 Verse of the Day:\n\nAs often as you eat this bread and drink the cup\, you
  proclaim the Lord’s death until he comes.  (1 Corinthians 11:26)\n\nHymn o
 f the Day:\n\n        313     Jesus Christ\, Our Blessed Savior\n\nColor:  
 Purple or White\n\n
