 us Christ\, our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, 
 one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia. All the ends o
 f the earth have seen the salvation of our God.  Alleluia.  (Psalm 98:3b)\n
 \nHymn of the Day:\n\n        34 Now Sing We\, Now Rejoice\n\nColor:  White
 \n\n
