 n        Isaiah 52:7-10\n\n        Hebrews 1:1-9\n\n        John 1:1-14\n\n
         Psalm 98\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        Exodus 33:18-23\, 3
 4:5-7\n\n        John 1:1-18\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty God\, grant 
