 ur old bondage under the yoke of sin\; through Jesus Christ our Lord\, who 
 lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\
 n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  When the time had fully come\, God sent 
 his Son\, born of a woman\, born under law\, to redeem those under law.  Al
 leluia.  (Galatians 4:4\,5a)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        35      Of the 
 Father’s Love Begotten or\n\n        33      All Praise to You\, Eternal Go
 d\n\nColor:  White\n\n
