 nations your one and only Son.  Guide us\, also\, who know him now by faith
 \, to come at last to the perfect joy of your heavenly glory\; through Jesu
 s Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one
  God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  We saw his star 
 in the east and have come to worship him.  Alleluia.  (Matthew 2:2b)\n\nHym
 n of the Day:\n\n        79      How Lovely Shines the Morning Star\n\nColo
 r:  White\n\n
