 e servants and stretch out the right hand of your power to defend us agains
 t all our enemies\; through Jesus Christ\, your Son\, our Lord\, who lives 
 and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVer
 se of the Day: \n\nJust as Moses lifted up the snake in the desert\, so the
