 ith you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Da
 y: \n\nJesus humbled himself and became obedient to death\, even death on a
  cross.  (Philippians 2:8b) \n\nHymn of the Day:\n        391     God Loved
  the World So that He Gave \n\nColor:  Purple \n\n
