 e merits and mediation of your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and 
 reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse o
 f the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  Now faith is being sure of what we hope for and ce
 rtain of what we do not see.  Alleluia.  (Hebrews 11:1)\n\nHymn of the Day:
