 ia.  You are my Son\, whom I love\; with you I am well pleased.  Alleluia. 
  (Mark 1:11b)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n\n        89      To Jordan’s River Came
  Our Lord or\n\n        88      To Jordan Came the Christ\, Our Lord\n\nCol
