 n        Isaiah 9:2-7\n\n        Titus 2:11-14\n\n        Luke 2:1-20\n\n  
       Psalm 96\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        Micah 5:2-5a\n\n     
    1 John 1:1-9\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty God\, you made this holy 
 night shine with the brightness of the true light.  Grant that as we have k
 nown on earth the wonder of that light\, we may also behold him in all glor
 y in the life to come\; through your only Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who
  lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.
 \n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  Today in the town of David a Savior has
  been born to you\; he is Christ the Lord.  Alleluia.  (Luke 2:11)\n\nHymn 
 of the Day:\n\n        38      From Heaven Above to Earth I Come or\n\n    
     37      Once Again My Heart Rejoices\n\nColor:  White\n\n
