 and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVer
 se of the Day\n\n     Alleluia. You are my Son\, whom I love\; with you I a
 m well pleased. Alleluia. (Mark 1:11b)\n\nHymn of the Day: \n\n     88 To J
 ordan Came the Christ\, Our Lord\n \n     89 To Jordan’s River Came Our Lor
 d\n\nColor: White
