 the Holy Spirit\, living and reigning\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Da
 y: \n\nAlleluia.  Holy\, holy\, holy is the Lord Almighty\; the whole earth
  is full of his glory.  Alleluia.  (Isaiah 6:3b) \n\nHymn of the Day:\n    
     177\, 178        Come\, Holy Ghost\, Creator Blest \n\nColor:  White \n
 \n
