  Genesis 15:1-6\n\n        Hebrews 11:1-3\,8-16\n\n        Luke 12:32-40\n\
 n        Psalm 33\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n\n        Haggai 1:2-14\n\n 
        Revelation 3:1-6\n\nPrayer of the Day:\n\nAlmighty and everlasting G
 od\, you are always more ready to hear than we to pray\, and to give more t
 han we either desire or deserve.  Pour upon us the abundance of your mercy\
