 cy cleanse our hearts and lips that\, free from doubt and fear\, we may eve
 r worship you\, one true immortal God\, with your Son and the Holy Spirit\,
  living and reigning\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nAlleluia.  Ho
 ly\, holy\, holy is the Lord Almighty\; the whole earth is full of his glor
 y.  Alleluia.  (Isaiah 6:3b)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n177\,178Come\, Holy Ghost
