DESCRIPTION:The Nativity of Our Lord—Christmas Day \n\nLessons and Psalm:\n
       Isaiah 52:7-10\n      Hebrews 1:1-9\n      John 1:1-14\n      Psalm 9
 8 \n\nPrayer of the Day: \n\nAlmighty God\, grant that the birth of your on
 e and only Son in the flesh may set us free from our old bondage under the 
 yoke of sin\; through Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you
  and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n\n
 Alleluia.  When the time had fully come\, God sent his Son\, born of a woma
 n\, born under law\, to redeem those under law.  Alleluia.  (Galatians 4:4\
 ,5a)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n     35      Of the Father’s Love Begotten or\n  
    33      All Praise to You\, Eternal God \n\nColor:  White
