 re\; for you live and reign with him and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now an
 d forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n\nAlleluia.  Alleluia.  Christ is risen! 
  He is risen indeed!  Alleluia.  I am the good shepherd\; I know my sheep a
 nd my sheep know me.  Alleluia.  (John 10:14)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n      37
 5               The King of Love My Shepherd Is \n\nColor:  White \n\n
