  present us at last holy and blameless before you\; through your Son\, Jesu
 s Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Spirit\, one
  God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nAlleluia.  Watch\, therefore\
 , for you do not know on what day your Lord is coming.  Alleluia.  (Matthew
  24:42)\n\nHymn of the Day:\n382My Hope Is Built on Nothing Less\n\nColor: 
