 r and the Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day: \n\
 nAs often as you eat this bread and drink the cup\, you proclaim the Lord’s
  death until he comes.  (1 Corinthians 11:26) \n\nHymn of the Day:\n       
  313             Jesus Christ\, Our Blessed Savior \n\nColor:  Purple or Wh
 ite \n\n
