DESCRIPTION:Fifth Sunday of Easter\n\nLessons and Psalm:\nActs 13:44-52\nRe
 velation 21:1-16\nJohn 13:31-35\nPsalm 145\n\nSupplemental Lectionary:\n1 S
 amuel 20:12-17\n1 Corinthians 13:1-13\n\nPrayer of the Day:\nO God\, you fo
 rm the minds of your faithful people in to a single will.  Make us love wha
 t you command and desire what you promise\, that among the many changes of 
 this world\, our hearts may ever yearn for the lasting joys of heaven\; thr
 ough your Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and t
 he Holy Spirit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\nAlleluia.
