 y always make our petitions according to your gracious will\; through your 
 Son\, Jesus Christ our Lord\, who lives and reigns with you and the Holy Sp
 irit\, one God\, now and forever.\n\nVerse of the Day:\n\nAlleluia.  Allelu
 ia.  Christ is risen!  He is risen indeed!  Alleluia.  If anyone loves me\,
  he will obey my teaching.  My Father will love him\, and we will come to h
 im and make our home with him.  Alleluia.  (John 14:23)\n\nHymn of the Day:
 \n\n        377     Dear Christians\, One and All\, Rejoice\n\nColor:  Whit
 e\n\n
